      <title>分析师称，随着消费疲软，阿根廷3月份通胀率将再次放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/argentina-march-inflation-slow-again-consumption-weakens-analysts-say-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社调查的分析师估计，阿根廷3月份的月通胀率可能小幅降至12%，这将标志着物价连续第三个月减速，并推动新自由主义总统哈维尔·米莱的经济改革举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/argentina-march-inflation-slow-again-consumption-weakens-analysts-say-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:27:18 GMT</pubDate>
